race.comment: UNQUESTIONABLY (7) is racing well and looks overdue for a win. Placed 3/6 including the last two. This suits and gets a chance to break through. SHREWSBURY ROAD (4) is another overdue. Placed fresh over 1400m then just missed over a mile. Has paced third-up and extra trip is a plus. Will be hard to hold out. PRESTIGE GEOFFREY (8) is much better than the last two suggest. Went back to the tail from the outside gate last time and never came on. Back in class and can improve sharply. HIGH TORQUE (9) was well off his best two back then ran a better race last time to place. Among the hopes here if he repeats that figure. BATTLE POINT (5) was fourth in similar grade two back then outclassed in a BM70 last time. Can atone.
